ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectPayments Received Under the Atlantic Groundfish Licence Retirement Program Remission Order, No. 2
PrecisPAYMENTS RECEIVED UNDER THE ATLANTIC GROUNDFISH LICENCE RETIREMENT PROGRAM REMISSION ORDER, NO. 2 in order to remit a portion of the federal income tax, employment insurance benefits repayments where applicable, and interest paid or payable thereon, in respect of the 1999 tax year, by fishers who received payments under the Atlantic Groundfish Licence Retirement Program.
